Generic single-database configuration for Alembic (Hands-On 7).

This folder tracks the schema history of college_db_orm as a chain
of three revisions, matching the exercise book's Hands-On 7 steps:

  1. initial_schema.py       - baseline: departments, students,
                                courses, enrollments, professors
                                (Task 1, Steps 92-97)
  2. add_is_active.py        - adds students.is_active
                                (Task 2, Steps 98-101)
  3. add_course_schedule.py  - adds the course_schedules table
                                (Task 2, Step 102)

See ../hands_on_7.sql for the full list of Alembic CLI commands
used to generate, apply, inspect and roll back these revisions.
